snippet.textDisplay: From the soul-stirring strains of classical ragas to the infectious beats of folk rhythms, music resonates deeply within the hearts of people on both sides of the border. It serves as a conduit for empathy, fostering connections that transcend geographic boundaries and fostering a shared sense of identity and belonging. In the harmonious notes of melody and rhythm, lies the promise of a brighter, more harmonious future, where the bonds forged through music continue to strengthen the ties, enriching lives and nurturing peace.
